      "title": "*gleubh-<div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\"></div>",
      "html": "<p>原始印欧语根，意为“撕裂，劈开”。&nbsp; </p><p>它构成了以下词语的全部或部分： <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of cleave \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/cleave\">cleave</a>（v.1）“用力分裂、分开或分割”； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of cleft \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/cleft\">cleft</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of clever \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/clever\">clever</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of clevis \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/clevis\">clevis</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of clove \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/clove\">clove</a>（n.2）“大蒜片”； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of glyptodon \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/glyptodon\">glyptodon</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of hieroglyphic \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/hieroglyphic\">hieroglyphic</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of petroglyph \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/petroglyph\">petroglyph</a>。</p><p>它是假设的来源/其存在的证据由以下提供：希腊语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">glyphe</i> “雕刻”， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">glyphein</i> “用刀挖空、切割、雕刻”； 拉丁语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">glubere</i> “剥皮、剥壳、剥离”； 古高地德语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">klioban</i>，古英语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">cleofan</i>，古挪威语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">kljufa</i> “劈开”，古挪威语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">klofi</i>，中古荷兰语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">clove</i> “裂缝”。</p>"
    }
